VULNERABILITY_CONFIG_PATH=
########################################################################################
## Parameter        		| VULNERABILITY_CONFIG_PATH
## Name             		| Vulnerability.json config file path
## Characteristics  		| If not provided then the -vp argument will not be passed to QSE Scan
##======================================================================================
## Default Value    		| (Empty value)
## Possible Values  		| <<cli_folder_path>>/vulnerability_severity.json
##======================================================================================